OPTOMA CORP (3565)  said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 27.03% to NT$479,736,000 from NT$377,665,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            479,736          377,665    
YOY%              27.03%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           2,607,662        2,411,885   
YOY%              8.12%  
=================================================================
 